race.description: Linx Finance Hcp (C1) - Heat Of The Rising Star
race.comment: LUNA JET (5) has found the line well in both runs back and looks ready to peak third-up. Blinkers go on, she draws close and gets in light. Top contender. KOTAISHI (1) returned in style when just missing at Canberra. Backs up quickly and should relish the extra ground with Keatings sticking. Main danger. BOOM IN THE DARK (3) was poor last time at Bathurst but had been building nicely before that. Worth forgiving and can run a place. SONIC SCENE (2) is rock-hard fit and back to a winning track and trip. Must be included. SECTORS (8) landed her maiden success last time out over 1200m at Wagga Riverside after a change in gear. Watch for any market confidence.
